body: 24 (return) [ When Julian, in a momentary panic, made the sign of the cross the d¾mons instantly disappeared, (Greg. Naz. Orat. iii. p. 71.) Gregory supposes that they were frightened, but the priests declared that they were indignant. The reader, according to the measure of his faith, will determine this profound question.]
